==Swedish==
'''skit-snack, ''et'''''
====Etymology====
[[skit]] (''shit'') + [[snack]] (colloquial for ''talk'' or ''speech'')

===Interjection===
#(''vulgar, slang'') [[bullshit]]!

===Noun===
#(''vulgar, slang'') [[Bullshit]]; blatantly false statements, generally made with intent to deceive.

